data.name: testText.Text
data.value:
--> Switch Router Power Line Off And On Again, then Click 'OK' Button Within Three Seconds.
--> If it did not work the first time wait until this Popup comes up again and repeat.
Attention: Static PC LAN IP settings are needed. IP:

data.name: labelGW.Text
data.value: 1. Switsh Router on and connect PC and Router with a Patch, better would be to put a HUB between PC and Router 2. Set up static PC LAN: IP:192.168.178.2 Mask: 255.255.0.0 3. Disable all other Devices that use IP Addresses on the PC 4. Disable Firewall 5. Click Start Upload
